1
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:22,960
(Halaw mula sa nobelang
"Counterattack" ni Chai Ji Dan)

2
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:27,880
(Episode 24, May Bahay Naman Ako)

3
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:36,160
Narinig ko kay Cheng Yu...

4
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,359
yung Wu Suo Wei...

5
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,000
ibinenta ang lumang bahay
na iniwan sa kanya ng kanyang mga magulang...

6
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:40,880
upang hilahin ang ilang mga string
para sa aming anak sa oras na ito.

7
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,480
Kaya ano?

8
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:44,760
Umaasa siya kay Chi Cheng.

9
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:46,040
Nang lumabas si Chi Cheng,

10
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,560
at gumaling ang kanyang kumpanya,

11
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:49,160
kaya niyang bilhin ang napakaraming bahay.

12
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,640
Madali mong sabihin yan.

13
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,440
Maaari kang bumili ng bahay,

14
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,880
ngunit maaari kang bumili ng mga alaala?

15
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,696
Punta tayo sa Cultural Square.

16
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,720
Bakit tayo pupunta dun?

17
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,200
Malalaman mo pagdating natin doon.

18
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,400
Ano ang gusto mo, bata?

19
00:02:13,401 --> 00:02:14,759
- Gusto ko ito.
- Sige.

20
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:15,760
Eto na.

21
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,760
- Magpasalamat ka.
- Salamat.

22
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,136
- Bahala ka.
- Narito ang bayad.

23
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,760
- Okay. salamat po.
- Maganda ang negosyo.

24
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,160
- Tara na.
- Hindi ako pupunta.

25
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:35,359
ikaw naman? Kamusta ang negosyo mo?

26
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,360
Okay naman ngayon.

27
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:42,840
Xiao Wu.

28
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:45,760
Ginang Chi.

29
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,840
bakit ka nandito?

30
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,520
Medyo harsh yung sinabi ko last time .

31
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:49,999
Huwag isapuso.

32
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,160
(Blowing Sugar Figure)

33
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,599
Kung may kailangan ka, sabihin mo sa akin.

34
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:54,736
bibigyan kita ng pera.
Huwag na kayong magtayo ng stall dito.

35
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:55,800
Hindi na kailangan, Mrs. Chi.

36
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:57,440
Nandito din ako para maranasan ang buhay.

37
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,720
Nakaka-depress din ang pagiging nasa opisina araw-araw .

38
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,416
Misis Chi,
nagmamadali ka bang umalis?

39
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,440
Kung hindi,

40
00:03:02,441 --> 00:03:03,601
Gagawin kitang sugar figure.

41
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:06,720
- Oo naman.
- Sige.

42
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:19,480
Halika na. Simulan na natin itong gawin.

43
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,440
Dito, Mrs. Chi.

44
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,680
Napakaganda nito.

45
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:58,016
Paano mo nalaman na ipinanganak ako
sa Year of the Rabbit?

46
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,040
Sinabi sa akin ni Chi Cheng.

47
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:01,160
Kung gaano ka maalalahanin.

48
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,160
Ano itong basura?

49
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:16,440
basura?

50
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,320
Subukan mong hipan ang isa para sa akin.

51
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,200
Sa tingin ko sa pagkakataong ito,

52
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,200
hindi na talaga natin sila mapipigilan.

53
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,760
Kasalanan mo ang lahat.

54
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,439
Kung hahayaan mo ang abogado ng pamilya
at ang Finance Department ng kumpanya...

55
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,760
tumulong ng kaunti,

56
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,360
baka makalabas na si Chi Cheng.

57
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:36,800
Pero wala kang gagawin.

58
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,000
Ito ay mahusay.

59
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,120
Ngayon, may utang kaming pabor sa kanya.

60
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,640
Bakit tayo may utang sa kanya?

61
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,080
Nakulong si Chi Cheng
dahil sa kanya.

62
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,440
Ito ang dapat niyang gawin.

63
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,120
Bukod,

64
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:49,200
hindi ko inaasahan...

65
00:04:49,201 --> 00:04:50,400
ang kuripot na lalaking ito...

66
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,080
para maging mapagbigay sa pagkakataong ito.

67
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,720
Wala kang magagawa.

68
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,720
anong ginagawa mo

69
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,240
Ikaw darn matanda.

70
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:05,680
Hindi ka ba nahihiya?

71
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,760
Ito ay medyo matamis.

72
00:05:07,761 --> 00:05:09,280
Kinain mo. Syempre ang sweet.

73
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,440
Subukan ito.

74
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,360
Dito.

75
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:19,560
Salamat po sir.

76
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,000
Bahala ka.

77
00:05:21,001 --> 00:05:23,880
(Blowing Sugar Figure)

78
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:28,240
Nakilala ko lang siya sa abogado.

79
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,680
Ano ang sinabi niya?

80
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:43,640
(I don't hate you.
I can't bear for you to do that)

81
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,360
"Hindi kita galit."

82
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,320
"Hindi ko kayang gawin mo yun."

83
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,600
Bukas ilalabas ang hatol.

84
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,600
Sabi ni Cheng Yu,
sabay tayong pupunta doon.

85
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,000
papasa ako.

86
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,720
Bukas na bukas ang stall ko
.

87
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,240
Paanong hindi ka makakapunta?

88
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,160
Kung lalabas si Chi Cheng,

89
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:33,840
ikaw ang unang tao...

90
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,120
gusto niyang makita.

91
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:38,280
Paano kung hindi siya makalabas?

92
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,480
Kayo ay pumunta sa aking lugar.

93
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,800
Sa ganoong pagkakataon,

94
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:56,640
Hindi ko talaga alam
kung paano ko haharapin ang mga magulang ni Chi Cheng.

95
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,160
Ninong, ninong.

96
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:22,079
Siya ay isang mabuting kaibigan ko
at ni Chi Cheng,

97
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,080
Xiao Shuai.

98
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,440
G. at Gng. Chi.

99
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,440
Huwag kang mag-alala.

100
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,800
Tiyak na magiging maayos si Chi Cheng.

101
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,160
Hindi naman ako nag-aalala.

102
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,919
Dapat kong hayaan ang brat na ito na mas magdusa.

103
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:32,920
Hindi ka nag-aalala?

104
00:07:32,921 --> 00:07:34,096
Umuwi ka na kung hindi ka nag-aalala.

105
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,240
Pumunta ka. umalis ka na.

106
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,480
Ayos lang, ninang.

107
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:45,440
(Ang First Prosecutor's Office)

108
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:47,640
(Blowing Sugar Figure)

109
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,039
(Anong nangyari? Anong ginagawa mo?)

110
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,240
(Nasaan siya? Okay lang ba siya?)

111
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:56,520
- Sir, isang sugar figure.
- Kunin mo ito sa iyong sarili.

112
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,416
(Lingchuan People's Procuratorate
First Prosecutor's Office)

113
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,440
Pwede ka nang pumunta.

114
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:20,080
Chi Cheng.

115
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,360
Chi Cheng!

116
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:22,400
Chi Cheng!

117
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:24,120
Huwag kang magsalita ng masama sa anak natin.

118
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,496
Ang dami na niyang pinagdaanan.

119
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,520
ako...

120
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,520
Buddy, tumaba ka na.

121
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,480
At pumayat ka.

122
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:37,400
kamusta ka na?

123
00:08:37,800 --> 00:08:39,240
ayos na ako ngayon. Pinasok niya ang sarili niya.

124
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,280
buti naman.

125
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:42,520
Anak.

126
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:43,880
- Nanay.
- Okay na ngayon.

127
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:45,520
Huwag kang mag-alala.

128
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:54,880
Nasaan si Wei Wei?

129
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:58,160
Sa oras na ito,
dapat ay nagbebenta pa siya ng kendi.

130
00:08:58,520 --> 00:08:59,520
Ipapaalam ko sa kanya ngayon.

131
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:13,680
Tatay.

132
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:15,760
Ibigay mo sa akin ang susi ng kotse.

133
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,640
Ang taong iyon ay sumuko.

134
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:36,560
Siya...

135
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,560
- Ninong, ninong.
- G. at Gng. Chi.

136
00:09:37,561 --> 00:09:38,656
Kung wala nang iba,
aalis na tayo.

137
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,680
Mauuna na kami.

138
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,360
Well...

139
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:49,640
(Maayos na si Chi Cheng ngayon)

140
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,200
Oo!

141
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:54,320
Tinakot mo ako hanggang sa mamatay.
baliw ka.

142
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:58,959
Gusto ko ito!

143
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,519
- Dito. May sapat na para sa lahat.
- Gusto ko ito!

144
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,879
- Huwag mong awayin ito.
- Gusto ko ito.

145
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:03,256
- Lahat ay nakakakuha ng isa.
- Salamat, ginoo.

146
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:04,679
- Salamat, ginoo.
- Kunin ito isa-isa.

147
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:05,680
Salamat po sir.

148
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:07,040
Tumingin sa akin.

149
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,000
Bakit dalawa ang nawawala?

150
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:17,640
Jiang Xiao Shuai,
ano ang ginagawa mo?

151
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,200
Guo Cheng Yu.

152
00:10:20,201 --> 00:10:21,896
Bakit hindi ka gumawa ng isang bagay
tungkol kay Jiang Xiao Shuai?

153
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:22,920
gumawa ng isang bagay?

154
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:24,680
- Halika!
- Halika!

155
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:28,800
Masama kayong mag-asawa!

156
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:31,160
Bini-bully mo ako
habang wala si Chi Cheng!

157
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,720
Tumigil ka!

158
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:35,760
Itigil ang pagbaril!

159
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:39,280
Pumunta ka.

160
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:42,800
Huwag kang lalapit sa akin.

161
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:49,240
Bakit nandito rin kayong dalawa?

162
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:51,520
Tara na.

163
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,160
Tulong!

164
00:10:58,800 --> 00:10:59,800
Iligtas mo ako!

165
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,320
Wag mong barilin sa mukha ko.

166
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,520
Masakit.

167
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,480
Ikaw...

168
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:26,999
Tulungan mo ako!

169
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,680
Sinisipa mo ako ng mga bastos kapag nakalugmok ako.

170
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:36,200
isang tao! Tulong!

171
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:43,920
Bumangon ka na.

172
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:48,880
Ilipat!

173
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,320
Cheng Yu!

174
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:23,920
Kunin ang malaking water ball na ito!

175
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,560
Ibaba mo ako, Cheng Yu.

176
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:00,960
Alam mo kung ano? Bago ka dumating,

177
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,440
sobrang binu-bully ako ng apat na yun .

178
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:04,719
Tinutukan nila ako ng tubig sa ulo
at sa bibig ko.

179
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:06,200
Hindi pa rin ako nakakakain ng hapunan ngayon.

180
00:13:06,280 --> 00:13:07,799
Thank God dumating ka...

181
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:08,840
at tinalo sila...

182
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,120
salamat po.

183
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:36,320
Bakit ka nagpapasalamat sa akin?

184
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:39,360
Sa relasyon natin,
bakit ka nagpapasalamat sa akin?

185
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:42,000
Dapat tayong magkaroon ng malinaw na mga account,
kahit na sa iyong sariling kapatid.

186
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,760
magkapatid ba tayo?

187
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,080
Mag-asawa kami.

188
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,479
Ang mga mag-asawa ba ay nagtatago ng malinaw na mga account?

189
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,480
anong ginagawa mo

190
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,800
Kaya alam mong mag-asawa tayo.

191
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:57,440
Tawagin mo akong Hubby.

192
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:00,760
Sabihin mo.

193
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,320
- Sabihin mo.
- Mawala!

194
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:04,560
- Sabihin mo.
- Mawala!

195
00:14:05,920 --> 00:14:06,920
Wag kang gumalaw.

196
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,680
Inaantok ako ngayon. Gusto kong matulog.

197
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:11,320
Matulog ka na.

198
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:18,280
Binabalaan kita, huwag subukan ang anumang bagay.

199
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:26,840
humiga ka.

200
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:39,160
Matulog ka na.

201
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,480
Da Wei, oras na para kumain.

202
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,200
Chi Cheng.

203
00:15:05,400 --> 00:15:06,400
Oras na para kumain.

204
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:20,080
Hindi pa siya gising?

205
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:30,680
anong ginagawa mo

206
00:15:31,040 --> 00:15:32,680
Tingnan ko kung buhay pa siya.

207
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:41,440
Buhay pa siya.

208
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:57,640
Hindi pa siya gising?

209
00:15:58,880 --> 00:15:59,880
Oo.

210
00:16:01,560 --> 00:16:03,040
Hindi
rin maaaring laktawan ni Chi Cheng ang kanyang pagkain.

211
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:05,280
Sa tuwing nagluluto kami,
inilalagay namin ito sa refrigerator.

212
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,080
Halos puno na ang refrigerator.

213
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:10,320
Dapat niyang bitawan muna si Da Wei.

214
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:13,400
Isang buong araw niyang hawak si Da Wei ,

215
00:16:13,800 --> 00:16:14,800
at hindi siya lalabas.

216
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:17,560
Sobrang cheesy.

217
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:19,840
Hindi ito gagawin.

218
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,760
Diretso kong ihahatid sa kanila.

219
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:23,840
Kainin mo to.

220
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:44,880
Isa kang tunay...

221
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:48,160
lalaki.

222
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:51,080
Sino siya?

223
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,720
Ninuno mo siya.

224
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:55,640
Tandaan na kumain.

225
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:00,560
Wait lang.

226
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,760
Sa wakas gising ka na.

227
00:17:16,760 --> 00:17:17,880
Dito. Subukan ito.

228
00:17:18,120 --> 00:17:19,120
Ginawa ito ni Cheng Yu.

229
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:21,880
Napakagaling magluto ni Cheng Yu.

230
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:24,120
Dito papasok ang masayang buhay ko.

231
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:25,760
Ang iyong kaligayahan...

232
00:17:25,840 --> 00:17:26,960
ay malapit nang matapos.

233
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:32,240
Hello, Cheng Yu?

234
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:34,240
Gising na siya.

235
00:17:34,241 --> 00:17:35,576
Hindi mo na kailangang sumama
at magluto.

236
00:17:35,600 --> 00:17:37,560
Okay. Sa wakas ay hindi ko na kailangang
abalahin pa iyon.

237
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:43,079
- Uy, iba ito!
- Okay lang, Wei Wei.

238
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:44,920
Dadalhin kita
sa isang Michelin-starred na restaurant.

239
00:17:45,120 --> 00:17:46,280
Maghintay ka. Pupunta ako doon.

240
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,440
Xiao Shuai.

241
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:49,440
May gagawin ako.

242
00:17:49,560 --> 00:17:50,560
Mag-order ng takeout para ngayong gabi.

243
00:17:50,560 --> 00:17:51,560
Kumain ka mag-isa.

244
00:17:52,560 --> 00:17:53,560
ako...

245
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:55,160
Kabutihan.

246
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:02,080
Pwede ba kitang samahan?

247
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:03,440
Pakiusap.

